   <title>Special string characters</title>
   <body>
      <p>
         <i>Halo: Reach</i>'s fonts include several unique icons and symbols, which are listed 
         below. Note that the game uses two sets of fonts. "TV Nord" is used for large portions 
         of the UI, including the scoreboard, HUD action prompts kill feed, and round cards. 
         "Eurostile" is used for most of the rest of the HUD, including the game variant name, 
         all scripted HUD widgets, and location names near the motion tracker.
      </p>
      
